     Installation from source code
=======================================
1.  Install g++, make, binutils, etc. for building from sources.
2.  Install QT4 version >= 4.6 with development packages (libqt4-dev).
3.  Install libusb-1.0 with development package.
4.  Install fxload.
5.  Install libgphoto2 with development package.
6.  Install libraw version >= 0.9.1 with development package.
7.  Install libtiff with development package.
8.  Install liblcms with development package.
9.  Unpack ccd.tar.bz2
10. Run ./configure and make to build program
